# Interview Questions

### What is Mean?

Average value of dataset.

### Difference between Mean and Median?

* Mean affected by outliers.
* Median not affected much.

### What is Standard Deviation?

Measures spread of data around mean.

### What is Correlation?

Measures relationship between variables.

### What is p-value?

Probability of getting observed results if Null Hypothesis is true.

### Difference between Type I and Type II Error?

| Type I         | Type II         |
| -------------- | --------------- |
| False Positive | False Negative  |
| Reject true H₀ | Accept false H₀ |

### When to use t-test?

Compare means of two groups.

### When to use ANOVA?

Compare means of three or more groups.

### When to use Chi-Square?

For categorical variables and association testing.

